Package: NpsychAssessmentTool
Type: Package
Title: UDS Battery Scores in Interactive Tables and Figures
Version: 0.3.2.9000
Description: Building on the NpsychBatteryNorms package,
    this package includes a Shiny application that makes 
    it easy to present UDS battery scores in a way useful
    to consensus diagnosis. Data can be imported as an
    .csv file or pulled directly from a REDCap database
    (`REDCapR` needed).
